    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Maxix Robotics，尽在掌握。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">欢迎来到 Maxix Robotics！以工程师身份在夜晚探索历史悠久的机器人工厂，并在风格化的恐怖环境中通过解谜完成任务。在环境中移动时，Maxix 工程师会发现许多秘密，请务必留意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/9583181f049aec4aceb8dc07f72ab2f2.poster.avif?t=1771616165\" width=460 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/9583181f049aec4aceb8dc07f72ab2f2.webm?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/9583181f049aec4aceb8dc07f72ab2f2.mp4?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>携带 D.O.T.T. 完成任务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从游戏中的终端获取属于你的个人 D.O.T.T.。D.O.T.T. 是你的私人同事，将帮助你在 Maxix Robotics 中导航。你是唯一的人类，所以请留意任何异常情况。我们的 B.O.T.T.s 会协助你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/e1700f33fbd8e7f020583cbf848c76cf.poster.avif?t=1771616165\" width=460 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/e1700f33fbd8e7f020583cbf848c76cf.webm?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/e1700f33fbd8e7f020583cbf848c76cf.mp4?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>探索 Maxix Robotics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">穿越 Maxix 设施的每个区域来更新你的 D.O.T.T.，使用你的朋友开门、完成任务，并确保符合 Maxix 的合规标准。D.O.T.T. 的终端与朋友的颜色相同，所以请仔细听取它的提示，它会在你探索 Maxix Robotics 时给你各种线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/cbed39e65a1b3a4f3e6444940d567399.poster.avif?t=1771616165\" width=460 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/cbed39e65a1b3a4f3e6444940d567399.webm?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/cbed39e65a1b3a4f3e6444940d567399.mp4?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>解开谜团</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一的限制是你的想象力，未完成任务不会受到 Maxix 管理层的欢迎。探索我们庞大设施的各个角落，同时注意隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/ebbc266baba688ddf9a4ffe013449487.poster.avif?t=1771616165\" width=460 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/ebbc266baba688ddf9a4ffe013449487.webm?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289120/extras/ebbc266baba688ddf9a4ffe013449487.mp4?t=1771616165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>免责声明：</strong> 游戏包含闪光灯、跳跃惊吓和大声噪音等恐怖游戏机制。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的终极目标是通过完成三种非常不同的谜题清理我们三翼的每一个区域。每个谜题都将挑战玩家，并需要使用不同技巧来避开巡逻设施的 B.O.T.T.s。玩家面前有许多秘密，需要保持警惕并专注于解开 Maxix Robotics 的谜团。</p>",
